Abuja – Tonto Dikeh has taken out time to appreciate her ex-boyfriend, saying regrets that he’s not the father of her child. Nollywood Actress, Tonto Dikeh yesterday, took to her Instagram to appreciate her ex-boyfriend, jeweller, Malivelihood A.K.A Michael Awujoola. She revealed the tattoo at her neck was done because of him and that she regrets that he is not the father of her son, Andre. Tonto wrote: “The tattoo at The back of my next.. I really was in Love, Dammit… The REAL MRX, We sure had so much fun..GOD BLESS YOUR HOME,YOU MADE ME SO HAPPY… EVERYDAY I REGRET WHY KING AINT YOURS.#EX APPRECIATION DAY” Source